data.description: Amazing over 2000 square foot Kamiah home on almost a quarter of an acre! So much potential with this one with a family room in the basement, and so much space to put a shop out back. New flooring throughout, paint, and a metal roof that will last. Close to schools, downtown, and more. Come and see this home while it lasts!
